channel.title: LandScape
channel.description:
Hello there, I Am trying to find out if anyone knows how to change the LandScape it shows on the Map when you walk.
My Friend on msn has the runescape landscape on his 317, it shows the colors and the circle of the Grand Exchange space there, i dont know how he added them...but thats why im trying to find out..
if anyone knows please tell me how do i get them or add them?
